@prefix sh:  <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#>.
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>.
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>.
@prefix ex:  <http://example.org/>.

# Is a mismatch because iri in JSON Schema is restricting the value to be an IRI, here the node itself becomes an IRI, lossy conversion

ex:Shape
    a           sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:nodeKind sh:IRI .